attractiveness or ability to pleasure your

00:00:12.650 --> 00:00:13.650
partner?

00:00:13.650 --> 00:00:17.820
Interestingly, humans have the largest penis
of any primate, both in absolute size and

00:00:17.820 --> 00:00:22.430
relative to body proportion...so you can be
proud of that! Through our evolutionary history,

00:00:22.430 --> 00:00:26.591
females likely developed an interest and preference
for penis shape and size - much like how female

00:00:26.591 --> 00:00:30.369
peacocks have a preference for a male with
stunning feathers. As a result, they chose

00:00:30.369 --> 00:00:35.360
mates with larger penises, ultimately passing
on those genes. This is know as sexual selection.

00:00:35.360 --> 00:00:40.040
It also may have been an advantage for males,
as a longer penis is more efficient at removing

00:00:40.040 --> 00:00:44.280
the sperm of rival males during intercourse.
The longer your depth of thrust, the better

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:47.470
semen displacement, ensuring your genes get
passed on.

00:00:47.470 --> 00:00:51.580
One particular study found that some women
experience more frequent vaginal orgasms with

00:00:51.580 --> 00:00:55.780
