to note that women experience different types

00:01:00.050 --> 00:01:04.920
of orgasms; in fact, vaginal and clitoral
orgasms may be completely separate phenomena

00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:09.530
- they use different nerves, and even stimulate
different areas of the brain. Even the coveted

00:01:09.530 --> 00:01:14.520
“G-Spot”, another sexually sensitive area
in women, is located only ⅓ of the way into

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:18.259
the vagina. Apart from this, many surveys
of women have found that they’re not nearly

00:01:18.259 --> 00:01:22.869
as concerned with size, as men might think,
and preferences vary. However, studies on

00:01:22.869 --> 00:01:26.869
