contact. Which may seem odd considering we

00:01:36.719 --> 00:01:41.750
wear clothes nowadays; but for our ancestors,
the genitals would have been visible. In the

00:01:41.750 --> 00:01:45.689
study, women were asked to rank the attractiveness
of males based on computer generated images

00:01:45.689 --> 00:01:50.030
reflecting different body types and penis
sizes. From this, it was clear that not only

00:01:50.030 --> 00:01:54.680
were taller and more fit men much more desirable,
but flaccid penis size played a role in their

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:59.479
perceived attractiveness too. The larger the
penis, the higher they were rated. But there

00:01:59.479 --> 00:02:05.280
was a limit - a flaccid penis larger than
about 7.6 cm and attractiveness began to diminish.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:10.540
It would seem a penis in proportion may be
most desirable. After all, over exaggerated

00:02:10.540 --> 00:02:15.030
